text: Sungai Kelugos, officially known in Malay as (sometimes ), is a settlement in Tutong District, Brunei. It is officially a village-level subdivision under the mukim or subdistrict of Keriam. The postcode for Sungai Kelugos is TB2741. == References == Category:Populated places in Brunei Category:Villages of Brunei
